			<h2><a href="/blog/chief-wine-officer/">Chief Wine Officer</a></h2>
			<h3>National Portrait Gallery, London | Published <time>14 November 2023</time> in <a href="https://mariothomas.com/categories/photos/">Photos</a> <a href="https://mariothomas.com/categories/aws/">AWS</a>  | 1 minute view | <a href="/blog/chief-wine-officer/"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Permalink" /></a></h3>
		</header>

		<p>Tonight I got an opportunity to speak at the <a href="https://www.chiefwineofficer.com/event/demystify-generative-ai-aws/">Chief Wine Officer</a> event hosted by AWS to an audience of customers about generative AI, the opportunities it creates, and how customers are using it to accelerate business outcomes.</p>

		
		
